VERSION 2 OF DUSTMAS2!

De_dustmas2 - By Lagmonster from UKMD
_v2 - Edited by Alias from UKCS

STORY:
On Dec 23rd, Moggie decided to give out $16000 to all the n00bs. But Major_Soulreaver had other ideas.. with all the Terrorists he could find he set out to stop MoggieXmas's plans!

Counter-terrorists - Protect the presents against the terrorists. Watch out for MoggieXmas's rushes!

Terrorists - You have only a short time to blow up the presents. If your lucky you will have been given $1600 by some n00b to make it abit easier for you. Watch out at short A as some n00b might be spamming nades!

Mapping - Lagmonster

Optimization - Alias

Beta Testers - DUNK, Wingnut, Major_Soulreaver, Manny, Retro and Team MX

Thanks - Thanks to Riley & Bling Bling for the MoggieXmas image

Thanks to Alias @ UKCS for helping optimize the map, bit of a disspointment the first version - but this time it's even better! Thankyou MOX @ UKCS for getting me intouch with your mappers :D

Thankyou to everyone posting the first version on forums and spreading the map around :) I did join up to a few and post some comments :D

Thanks to MoggieX for hosting the first version on UKMD and giving it a test!

Hope you enjoy the map over christmas!

UKMD Team MX - HAPPY XMAS N00BS !
